data.description: Location, Location, Location! Come check out this spacious split level on a equally spacious lot.  It is conveniently located near shopping, restaurants, minutes from Wright Patterson Air Force Base and Interstate access.  Many updates have already been done for you to include: Roof Jan. 2022, Bathroom updates 2023, Heating and cooling 2022, New countertops 2023 and New range hood 2023. Don't wait! Come make this home yours!*Room sizes are approximate
